    <!-- Updates Section -->
    <div class="status-updates text-start">
      <h2 class="h5 mt-4">Latest Updates</h2>
      <div class="mt-2">
        <p><strong>Sunday, March 22nd<br>9:00PM - 10:00PM ET</strong></p>
        <p>MembersFirst will be performing scheduled maintenance starting at 9:00PM ET on Sunday, March 22nd and finishing by 10:00PM ET.
<br><br>
During this 1-hour window, we will update our hosting environment which unfortunately requires taking our hosted solutions offline. This will affect access to your website, blast email, mobile app, and other MembersFirst-hosted services. If you have scheduled a blast email during this period, it will be paused and restarted after the maintenance window. Emails and messages will only be delayed, not lost.
<br><br>
Thank you for your understanding as we continually work to improve and secure our hosting environment for you.</p>
      </div>
